### Example 1: Initializing Vertex AI and Generative Model

```typescript
import { getVertexAI, getGenerativeModel, VertexAI, GenerativeModel, GenerateContentRequest, GenerateContentResult } from 'firebase';

// Initialize Firebase app (assuming you have already set up Firebase)
import { initializeApp } from 'firebase/app';
